==Long-term effects==

Rehabilitative gains in motor control through treatment with the ADELI Suit are typically retained after the intensive course is completed.{{cn|date=December 2012}} Research on groups of children with the ADELI Suit therapy has shown long-term retention of skills once their therapy program ceased.{{cn|date=December 2012}} However, further research is still needed into all the long-term effects.

